data.title: Suwayda
data.meta_description: As-Suwayda As-Suwayda (also spelled As-Suweida, as-Suwaydā’, Sweida, or Swaida) is a predominantly Druze city in southern Syria and is the capital of the As-Suwayda Governorate.
